YUM-RepoQuery 

This package provides a means of querying a YUM repository for package
information, using the standard 'repoquery' command.

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make test
	make install


DEPENDENCIES

repoquery.


